PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/1.3/Brick#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX s223: <https://w3id.org/saref#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?zoneLabel ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint
WHERE {
  # ---- Zones ----------------------------------------------------
  ?zone a brick:Zone .
  OPTIONAL { ?zone rdfs:label ?zoneLabel . }

  # ---- Case 1: Property directly attached to the Zone -------------
  { ?zone brick:hasProperty ?prop . }

  UNION

  # ---- Case 2: Property reachable via a RoomDomainSpace in exactly two steps ----
  {
    # Two arbitrary hops from the Zone to a RoomDomainSpace (any direction)
    ?zone (<>|^<>){2} ?roomSpace .
    ?roomSpace a brick:RoomDomainSpace .
    ?roomSpace brick:contains ?prop .
  }

  # ---- Property details ------------------------------------------
  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .

  # external reference – alc endpoint (writable = false)
  ?prop brick:externalReferenceAlcEndpoint ?alcRef .
  ?alcRef brick:writable false ;
          brick:hasEndpoint ?alcEndpoint .

  # external reference – mpc endpoint (writable = false)
  ?prop brick:externalReferenceMpcEndpoint ?mpcRef .
  ?mpcRef brick:writable false ;
          brick:hasEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint .
}
ORDER BY ?zoneLabel ?propLabel
